{"tid":1530200,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣/IT人請入 不如整個事件資料庫","createTime":"2019-09-02T01:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T03:29:08.000Z","uid":155292,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"19666036b2d90d19f1c79d6437ca94657fabc728","tid":1530200,"uid":155292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:40:57.000Z","msg":"接近三個月以來太多事發生<br />\n資訊太多太亂<br />\n<br />\n好多時就咁一兩張相傳出嚟，<br />\n已經搞唔清楚係邊度、幾時嘅事<br />\n<br />\n可能亦都係咁樣間接導致BBC炒車事件(POPO汽油彈改圖)發生？<br />\n<br />\n不如整個好似Wikipedia咁嘅小型資料庫<br />\n按每一日嘅重大事件去分類<br />\n裏面除咗有手足影嘅相、片 (仲要有埋擁有人tg，方便外媒搵片主)，亦都可以link返相關嘅外媒報道<br />\n<br />\n等關注事件嘅人可以好容易睇到一啲可信嘅資料<br />\n(之前見過有人send個list出嚟係警暴事件，可以base on個list每一件事都可以再㩒入去睇詳細嘅描述同埋相片)<br />\n<br />\n在申請翻個吸睛嘅URL<br />\n<a href=\"http://例如hkpoliceviolence.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82hkpoliceviolence.com&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FcwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=b9c3fc9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">例如hkpoliceviolence.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://hongkongsos.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhongkongsos.com&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FcwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=953030db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hongkongsos.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://hongkonghumanitariancrisis.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhongkonghumanitariancrisis.com&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FcwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=4a51029e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hongkonghumanitariancrisis.com</a><br />\n<br />\n我唔識IT、亦都唔識整圖<br />\n只係識少少英文，如果有需要可以做翻譯工作<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"01264e23a04092fe6f7048345906a96173f47a22","tid":1530200,"uid":85451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:57:05.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n要搵啲developer出黎 整個web"},{"pid":"313aa32c6a8727595ee3241fb3bede4953e97d98","tid":1530200,"uid":249001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:18:13.000Z","msg":"已有相關網頁整緊。"},{"pid":"82c07b77106b16463babe726d1cd36df399f38ca","tid":1530200,"uid":61084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:29:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2F&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FcwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=ca21f714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/</a><br />\n<br />\n要人幫手"}]}